data.description: Beautifully maintained rarely available & highly desirable first floor condo with large windows and sliders that blur the lines between interior living and outdoor wildlife, ooze that soothing Florida sunlight. LOCATED minutes and easily accessible by secondary roads to almost everything. Relax and watch in wonder at amazing Florida sunrises and sunsets from a generous screened lanai overlooking a nature wood area. 2 generous bedrooms plus an addition flex room for your office or home gym. Cozy formal dining room features a bay style window with panoramic views to a preserve. Assigned carport and an additional exterior 4x5 owners closet 10 steps from your front door. chairs, New AC system, New roof, New Premium GE Stainless Steele Range and Microwave. Banyan Trace amenities include, a heated community pool and hot tub, gazebo, bocce, tennis courts, BBQ - Picnic area, Cabana, Clubhouse,  exercise Room, internet Access, WiFi, water, and sewer and insurances. Great community with even greater neighbors. PETS NOT ALLOWED.
